-----Original Message-----
From: MICHAEL TURNER [mailto:airmike(-at-)verizon.net] 
Subject: [VB] dashboard fabric (-at-) speaker

After asking I was given the bag which I washed several 
times to soften it slightly. I then cut it to fit the dash opening, actually
just 
slightly larger. Then went to ACE hardware where I purchased some very light
small mesh 
plastic screen materiel and trimmed it to the same size as my dash sized
burlap 
"patch". Took duct tape, went around the edges to tape the two together and
then 
Stapled the cover in a few places to reinforce it. 
